00:53:30,624 --> 00:53:31,625
Stowing away.

781
00:53:33,752 --> 00:53:36,212
No wonder you're not dressed warmly.

782
00:53:37,172 --> 00:53:39,257
It's freezing this time of the year
out in the ocean.

783
00:53:40,175 --> 00:53:41,801
Stowing away often
isn't something to brag about.

784
00:53:42,469 --> 00:53:44,512
At least I have experience.

785
00:53:45,847 --> 00:53:47,682
Can you speak Chinese?

786
00:53:47,766 --> 00:53:48,767
No.

787
00:53:49,267 --> 00:53:50,268
Can you?

788
00:53:51,436 --> 00:53:52,437
Of course not.

789
00:54:14,084 --> 00:54:16,628
You must be tired
coming all the way out here.

790
00:54:17,671 --> 00:54:20,173
You two are going out
on the Manyang, right?

791
00:54:20,924 --> 00:54:21,925
Who's calling?

792
00:54:22,676 --> 00:54:24,844
STRAW

793
00:54:27,514 --> 00:54:28,515
Yes.

794
00:54:31,893 --> 00:54:34,270
-What?
-Sir, her cover has been blown.

795
00:54:34,354 --> 00:54:37,816
Those guys found out
the police sent someone undercover.

796
00:54:37,899 --> 00:54:40,694
They have to leave Korea no matter what,
so they'll go to a different port.

797
00:54:40,777 --> 00:54:42,737
Which one of you is here because of Straw?

798
00:54:43,863 --> 00:54:46,992
Nice to meet you. Let's go.

799
00:55:01,756 --> 00:55:02,882
Get in now!

800
00:55:08,430 --> 00:55:11,266
-Are you okay?
-I'm fine. Give me some handcuffs.

801
00:55:11,349 --> 00:55:12,559
Jeez, you scared me.

802
00:55:12,642 --> 00:55:13,685
Go after them!

803
00:55:34,289 --> 00:55:36,332
MANPYEONG PORT

804
00:55:47,469 --> 00:55:48,678
CHARGING

805
00:55:49,429 --> 00:55:50,680
ASSISTANT INSPECTOR
OH SU-HYEON

806
00:55:51,556 --> 00:55:53,266
-Yes, Captain?
-Su-hyeon.

807
00:55:53,808 --> 00:55:55,435
I'm chasing a suspect car
at Manpyeong Port.

808
00:55:55,518 --> 00:55:56,895
Check for any nearby ports.

809
00:55:56,978 --> 00:55:57,979
Just a moment, sir.

810
00:55:59,439 --> 00:56:00,440
Hurry, Su-hyeon.

811
00:56:02,901 --> 00:56:05,653
There's Ingok Port.

812
00:56:05,737 --> 00:56:07,739
It's 15 kilometers north of where you are.

813
00:56:07,822 --> 00:56:08,823
Ingok Port?

814
00:56:16,456 --> 00:56:17,999
Request local backup

815
00:56:18,083 --> 00:56:19,959
and tell the Coast Guard
to go to Ingok Port.

816
00:56:20,043 --> 00:56:21,544
Yes, sir.

817
00:57:58,224 --> 00:57:59,601
PUNGEO

818
00:59:05,041 --> 00:59:06,751
Gong Jin-uk!

819
00:59:53,006 --> 00:59:54,257
Jang Jae-gyeong.

820
00:59:55,216 --> 00:59:58,928
You're under arrest for violating
the Narcotics Control Act.

821
00:59:59,846 --> 01:00:00,930
You damn druggie.

822
01:01:00,114 --> 01:01:02,033
-Come with me.
-Section Chief Jung!

823
01:01:02,116 --> 01:01:04,452
Who are you calling a suspect?
Come with me.

824
01:01:04,535 --> 01:01:07,163
You just want to believe
that Jun-seo wanted it.

825
01:01:07,246 --> 01:01:08,331
I'm right, so shut up.

826
01:01:08,414 --> 01:01:09,624
No, you shut up!

827
01:01:09,707 --> 01:01:11,584
I'm publishing this article
no matter what.

828
01:01:11,668 --> 01:01:13,920
I'm going to kill you
as soon as I get out!

829
01:01:14,003 --> 01:01:16,130
They should be our feat.

830
01:01:16,214 --> 01:01:18,216
-You're unbelievable.
-You haven't changed at all.

831
01:01:18,299 --> 01:01:21,010
Why haven't you come to your senses?

832
01:01:21,094 --> 01:01:22,428
Park Tae-jin.

833
01:01:22,970 --> 01:01:24,514
I'll do anything you want.

834
01:01:24,597 --> 01:01:25,973
-Jong-soo.
-Hey.

835
01:01:26,057 --> 01:01:27,308
Jong-soo killed him.

836
01:01:27,392 --> 01:01:29,102
He said he was going to kill Jun-seo.

837
01:01:29,185 --> 01:01:31,187
Did you say you'd help him, sir?

838
01:01:32,355 --> 01:01:33,606
Of course, I tried toâ€¦

839
01:01:33,690 --> 01:01:36,401
He leeched off his friends
and delivered drugs.

840
01:01:36,484 --> 01:01:40,071
That was his pathetic life,
so get it together.

841
01:01:40,154 --> 01:01:42,949
They found DNA
under Park Jun-seo's fingernail.

842
01:01:43,032 --> 01:01:44,033
You know who he is, right?

843
01:01:44,117 --> 01:01:46,452
The revenge you wanted to get for Jun-seoâ€¦

844
